  "c.h":"the ether — what they say between moves",
  "p.eye":"Play a mind","p.h":"Sit down for a game against one of my players","p.p":"Pick a mind and play a real game. If it is mid-tournament, you join the queue — you get an email when it frees up and your turn comes.","p.mail":"your email","p.btn":"Play / join the queue","p.note":"Your email is only for the queue notification. No spam, no accounts.",
  foot:"the engine plays non-stop on its own server · python-chess", min:"min", busy:"at a table", free:"free", play:"play", queue:"queued"},
